                    "body": "For what it's worth, RSPM hosts full binary R packages, if you can install from there. I don't know if they still support xenial though.\r\n\r\nIn arrow 4.0, you can set ARROW_PARQUET=OFF to turn off parquet support; parquet is what requires thrift.",
